AGI - The U.S. Central Command successfully hired and destroyed four drones launched by Houthi terrorists in Yemen yesterday. The attacks were aimed at a Coalition ship and an American warship engaged in self-defense on the Red Sea. There were no reported injuries or damage to U.S. ships or the coalition.
